Reverse an Array:

Link : https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/problems/reverse-an-array/1

Implementation:

class Solution {
    public void reverseArray(int arr[]) {
        int i=0;
        int j =arr.length-1;
        while(i<=j) {
            int temp=arr[i];
            arr[i] = arr[j];
            arr[j]=temp;
            j--;
            i++;
        }
        return;
    }
}

Time complexity : O(n)
Space complexity : O(1)
